Rating: 4
I used this recipe for lamb loin chops, and my husband gave it the coveted "thumbs up". After marinating, I seared the chops and roasted them in the oven @ 375. Next time, I'll lower the temp, and roast them a little slower. I served them with the white bean recipe on this site that is paired with lamb shanks. Also delicious!

Rating: 4
i cant believe how well this recipe turned out. I broiled for longer than 7 minutes and still chops turned out juicy and flavorful. I was so pleasantly surprised!!! definitely worth trying for a quick weeknight meal.

