Quite tasty. This recipe could not be any easier. A great recipe to fall back on when you don't have a lot of time.

Rating: 3
Simple and really quite delicious..who could ask for anything more? This is as close to a perfect marinade for lamb that I have ever come across. Cooking time was a little off (we have a gas grill) they were perfect for me (medium rare to rare) but too pink for my husband. Gas grill users might need to adjust the cooking time somewhat. We prepared this to celebrate the coming of Spring in beautiful Nashville after a long unusually cold winter (we are rushing it a bit!). Next time we have this wonderful dish we will not need the sweaters and blankets. A real keeper..thanks Epicurious! This web site is a cooks dream come true.

